434
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:57,940
 Znači, ako ja primjećam

435
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,940
 što moj suprug sve radi

436
00:30:59,940 --> 00:31:01,860
 i ako je moj suprug

437
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:03,400
 meni nekako

438
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:06,180
