447
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:21,300
 Moja zubarica rekla

448
00:31:21,300 --> 00:31:23,520
 nazvala me moj hrve

449
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,280
 za vrijeme dok su bila kod nje,

450
00:31:25,280 --> 00:31:26,700
 a inače mi je ona i prijateljica.

451
00:31:26,700 --> 00:31:29,400
 I sad ja tamo gugučem.

452
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,180
 On kaže,

453
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,480
 je tog čera zvala?

454
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,440
 Ja kažem, ne muž.

455
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:33,620
 Muž!

456
00:31:33,620 --> 00:31:35,600
 On se sva izbezomila.

457
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:37,540
 A to, inače,

458
00:31:37,540 --> 00:31:39,360
 dečki baš trebali tog gugutanje.

459
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:41,100
 A misli, teba, ma, moj muž,

460
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:42,740
 jadam šta će navikao se već.

461
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:44,540
 Već mu je to postao tako i prirodno.

462
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:47,260
 Mislim, ne bi ja to od njega tražila,

463
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:48,900
 odnosno ne bi ja tako s njima razgovarala

464
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:50,840
 da mu to smeta.

465
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:53,640
 činica je da je o malo onak

466
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:55,460
 nekim ljudima idemo na žinicu.

467
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:56,960
 U svakom slučaju,

468
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,220
 ne znam zašto sam to spomenula,

469
00:31:58,220 --> 00:31:59,400
 s čim je to bilo povezano.

470
00:31:59,400 --> 00:31:59,920
 Na vezi.

471
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:02,760
 Ok, da vidim šta sam još

472
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:06,260
 htjela reći.

473
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:07,600
 Aha, htjela sam reći

474
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:09,060
 o sve tiče očekivanja cura.

475
00:32:09,060 --> 00:32:11,100
 Nekaj stvari se jako promjene.

476
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:13,140
 I zapravo, svaki brak ima

477
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,780
 svoje brojne izazove.

478
00:32:15,780 --> 00:32:17,340
