482
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:27,500
 Ono, nema nekakvih velikih svađa,

483
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:28,880
 ne znam, problema,

484
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:31,820
 on pije ili izlazi ili tako dalje,

485
00:32:31,820 --> 00:32:34,120
 ili žena neke svoje probleme,

486
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:35,880
 nego ono sve funkcionira,

487
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,920
 a zapravo ništa ne funkcionira.

488
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:39,560
 Odnosno, ti više ne poznaješ

489
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:40,740
 tog čovjeka pored sebe

490
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:42,480
 ili on ne poznaje tu ženu pored sebe.

491
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:43,580
 I što recimo,

492
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:45,360
 to je ovaj vam lockdown

493
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:47,340
 jako dobro pokazao,

494
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:50,120
 znači ljudi su ispaljivali na živce.

495
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:51,580
 Ljudi ne mogu biti doma.

496
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:54,960
 Ono, šta da radim doma?

497
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:57,020
 Šta da pričam sa?

498
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:59,660
 I tek onda shvatiš koliko su se udaljio.

499
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:01,000
 I taj lockdown, ja mislim,

500
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:04,080
 u sve svoje grozote

501
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:06,860
 donio jednu dobru stvar,

502
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:09,740
 a to je da su svi ljudi posvijestili

503
00:33:09,740 --> 00:33:11,220
 da neke stvari nisu okej.

504
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:13,500
 I nadam se, potrašili pomoć

505
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:15,640
 ili počeli raditi na svom braku.

506
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:18,600
 Dogodi se da tako brak lijepo funkcionira

507
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:21,180
 i onda kad djeca se poudavaju požene,

508
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:22,780
 onda se ljudi rastanu.

509
00:33:22,780 --> 00:33:24,180
 Jer shvate,

510
00:33:24,180 --> 00:33:25,120
 i onda kažu

511
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:28,440
 to nije čovjek za kojeg sam se ja udala.

512
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:29,380
 Pa naravno da nije.

513
00:33:29,380 --> 00:33:30,840
 Pa ljudi se mijenjaju.

514
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,440
 I bilo bi skroz i pogrešno očekivati

515
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:34,680
 da je čovjek isti

516
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,480
 prije 15 godina

517
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,760
 i danas,

518
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:38,840
 ili prije 30 godina,

519
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,020
 ili prije 40 godina.

520
00:33:40,020 --> 00:33:41,660
 Bogu hvala da se mijenjamo

521
00:33:41,660 --> 00:33:42,740
 i trebamo se mijenjati.

522
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:43,860
 Na bolje, naravno,

523
00:33:43,860 --> 00:33:45,180
 ali sigurno da imamo

524
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,040
 i neke druge stvari.

525
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,580
 Mi kad kažemo ono,

526
00:33:47,580 --> 00:33:48,840
 poznajem ga ko,

527
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:49,540
 ne znam,

528
00:33:49,540 --> 00:33:50,920
 koja je usporedba,

529
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:54,060
 time na neki način

530
00:33:54,060 --> 00:33:55,540
 i ograničavamo tu osobu

531
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:57,120
 da ne može postati netko drugi.

532
00:33:58,820 --> 00:34:01,060
 Mislim da kao što sebi dajemo priliku

533
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:02,200
 da rastemo,

534
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,580
 da tako treba dati priliku

535
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:04,500
 i ovome drugome.

536
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,980
 I još jedna stvar,

537
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:08,360
 znam puno cura

538
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:11,960
 koje su imale predivne dečke,

539
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,700
 pa onda zaručnike,

540
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:15,720
 a koji nisu bili u vjeri.

541
00:34:15,720 --> 00:34:18,120
 I nije im to smetalo,

542
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:18,700
 ono,

543
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:19,980
 dobri su bili dečki

544
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:20,600
 i stvarno,

545
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:20,780
 ono,

546
00:34:20,780 --> 00:34:21,300
 vole se

547
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:22,120
 i sve super

548
00:34:22,120 --> 00:34:23,240
 i nema nikakvih problema,

549
00:34:23,240 --> 00:34:24,680
 ali kad su ušli u brak,

550
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:26,200
 to je postao jako veliki problem.

551
00:34:26,200 --> 00:34:29,540
 Jer vi morate imati konsenzus

552
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,160
 kako ćete odgledati djecu,

553
00:34:31,160 --> 00:34:33,960
 kako ćete živjeti kroz život,

554
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:35,600
 koliko ćete se oslanjati na Boga.

555
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:37,740
 I sad nije još problem

556
00:34:37,740 --> 00:34:38,840
 ako je čovjek otvoren

557
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:40,460
 ili mu ne smetali,

558
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:41,320
 podržava,

559
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,460
 ali najčešće se događa

560
00:34:43,460 --> 00:34:44,360
 da mu smeta

561
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:47,340
 i da zapravo su djeca

562
00:34:47,340 --> 00:34:49,500
 rascijepina između mame i tate,

563
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:52,920
 ha i sama je žena

564
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:57,600
 negako teško joj je živjeti.

565
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:59,440
 Dakle, ako imate izbora,

566
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:01,080
 ja vjerujem,

567
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:02,200
 i ima jako puno ljudi

568
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:03,160
 koji su se obratili,

569
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:03,940
 upoznali Boga,

570
00:35:03,940 --> 00:35:05,060
 ali ako imate izbora,

571
00:35:05,060 --> 00:35:07,000
 i ako misli zapravo da

572
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,580
 to što nije u vjeri

573
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:11,700
 ne znači puno znači

574
00:35:11,700 --> 00:35:13,440
 i znači će jednog dana.

