00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:17,700
 i nekako nisam više

854
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,580
 ko prije.

855
00:41:18,580 --> 00:41:19,800
 Nadala sam se najviše

856
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,580
 da će mi dijete imat društvo,

857
00:41:21,580 --> 00:41:21,860
 ono,

858
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:23,220
 kak si nazbilo četvrlo

859
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:24,220
 i znam koliko je to,

860
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:26,300
 kakav je to veliki blagoslov.

861
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:27,780
 Sad već ima deveti pol,

862
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:28,320
 što je to?

863
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:29,840
 će biti igračka,

864
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:31,320
 ne, to neće više biti društvo.

865
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,600
 Tako da,

866
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,800
 ali i dalje molim,

867
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:35,760
 jer vidim da kroz tu molitvu

868
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:37,220
 me Bog mijenja

869
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,900
 i mijenja neke druge stvarnosti

870
00:41:38,900 --> 00:41:39,560
 u životu,

871
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:40,700
 u mom životu.

872
00:41:40,700 --> 00:41:42,760
 Evo, mislim da sam malo prekadašla,

873
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:43,780
 a evo ti veću zaključiti.

874
00:41:43,780 --> 00:41:44,660
 Prosti, pre Stjepena.

